caption:
Happy Birthday to #GraemeObree one of my biggest hero's growing up. Obree was/is a true visionary, innovator and extraordinary athlete
Taking the hour record twice in '93 and 94'.
Life has not been easy for Obree but he has risen to every challenge thrown at him so far. Have an awesome day Graeme Obree.
